text: Funtovo-1 () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Funtovsky Selsoviet, Privolzhsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 1,064 as of 2010. There are 55 streets. == Geography == It is located 13 km from Astrakhan, 14 km from Nachalovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Privolzhsky District, Astrakhan Oblast
title: Funtovo-1
